{
  "title": "Eden Interlay Proxy Dashboard (Testing)",
  "description": "Real-time monitoring of the Redis Direct proxy path.",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 3000000000000001,
      "definition": {
        "title": "About",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 3000000000000002,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "## Eden Interlay Direct Proxy\n\nDefault Redis traffic path:\n\n### Template variables\n- `$interlay_uuid`: filter by interlay\n- `$endpoint_uuid`: filter by endpoint\n- `$endpoint_kind`: filter by protocol (always `redis` on direct path)\n- `$eden_node_uuid`: filter by Eden node\n- `$client_ip`: filter by client IP (note: not a label on most proxy.* metrics)\n\n### Path scope\nWidgets show only metrics emitted by the direct path.",
              "background_color": "white",
              "font_size": "14",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 12,
              "height": 4
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 5
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3000000000000010,
      "definition": {
        "title": "Overview",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 3000000000000011,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "**At-a-glance health.** Active connections, throughput, p99 latency, error rate. If any tile is red, jump to the corresponding section below.",
              "background_color": "gray",
              "font_size": "12",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000012,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Active Connections",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "conns",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.active_connections{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}",
                      "aggregator": "last"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "conns",
                      "alias": "Conns"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 2,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000013,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Requests/sec",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "rate",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.requests_total{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}.as_rate()",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "rate",
                      "alias": "req/s"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "custom_unit": "req/s",
              "precision": 0
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 4,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000014,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Overhead p99",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "p99",
                      "query": "p99:eden.proxy.overhead_duration_microseconds{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "p99",
                      "number_format": {
                        "unit": {
                          "type": "canonical_unit",
                          "unit_name": "microsecond"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 100,
                      "palette": "white_on_green"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 500,
                      "palette": "white_on_yellow"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "value": 500,
                      "palette": "white_on_red"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "precision": 0
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 6,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000015,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Errors/sec",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "err",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.errors_total{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}.as_rate()",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "err",
                      "alias": "err/s"
                    }
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 0.01,
                      "palette": "white_on_green"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 1,
                      "palette": "white_on_yellow"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "value": 1,
                      "palette": "white_on_red"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 8,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000016,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Connection Failures/sec",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "fail",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.connection_failures_total{$interlay_uuid,$eden_node_uuid}.as_rate()",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "fail",
                      "alias": "fail/s"
                    }
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 0.01,
                      "palette": "white_on_green"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 0.5,
                      "palette": "white_on_yellow"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "value": 0.5,
                      "palette": "white_on_red"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 10,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3000000000000020,
      "definition": {
        "title": "Latency Breakdown",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 3000000000000021,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "**Latency attribution.** `comparable_request = endpoint + overhead` for batches with comparable timing. Use the stacked view to see whether spikes come from backend dispatch or proxy overhead. `request_duration` covers all batches (incl. those without comparable timing).",
              "background_color": "gray",
              "font_size": "12",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 3,
              "height": 7
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000022,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Endpoint dispatch + Proxy overhead (avg, \u03bcs)",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "max",
                "value"
              ],
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "alias": "Endpoint dispatch",
                      "formula": "endpoint",
                      "style": {
                        "palette": "classic",
                        "palette_index": 1
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "endpoint",
                      "query": "avg:eden.proxy.endpoint_duration_microseconds{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "dog_classic",
                    "order_by": "values",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  },
                  "display_type": "line"
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "alias": "Proxy overhead",
                      "style": {
                        "palette": "green",
                        "palette_index": 5
                      },
                      "formula": "overhead"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "overhead",
                      "query": "avg:eden.proxy.overhead_duration_microseconds{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "dog_classic",
                    "order_by": "values",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  },
                  "display_type": "line"
                }
              ],
              "yaxis": {
                "label": "Latency (\u03bcs)",
                "scale": "linear",
                "include_zero": true
              },
              "markers": [
                {
                  "label": "\u00a0Warning: 100\u03bcs\u00a0",
                  "value": "y = 500",
                  "display_type": "warning dashed"
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 3,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 9,
              "height": 4
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000023,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Request duration (p50 / p99, all batches)",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "max",
                "value"
              ],
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "alias": "p50",
                      "formula": "p50"
                    },
                    {
                      "alias": "p99",
                      "formula": "p99"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "p50",
                      "query": "p50:eden.proxy.request_duration_microseconds{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}"
                    },
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "p99",
                      "query": "p99:eden.proxy.request_duration_microseconds{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "cool",
                    "order_by": "values",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  },
                  "display_type": "line"
                }
              ],
              "yaxis": {
                "label": "Latency (\u03bcs)",
                "scale": "linear",
                "include_zero": true
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 3,
              "y": 4,
              "width": 5,
              "height": 3
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000024,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Bytes read / written (MB/s)",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "max",
                "value"
              ],
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "alias": "Read (MB/s)",
                      "formula": "read / 1048576"
                    },
                    {
                      "alias": "Written (MB/s)",
                      "formula": "written / 1048576"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "read",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.bytes_read_total{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}.as_rate()"
                    },
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "written",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.bytes_written_total{$interlay_uuid,$endpoint_uuid,$endpoint_kind,$eden_node_uuid}.as_rate()"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "cool",
                    "order_by": "values",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  },
                  "display_type": "area"
                }
              ],
              "yaxis": {
                "label": "MB/s",
                "scale": "linear",
                "include_zero": true
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 8,
              "y": 4,
              "width": 4,
              "height": 3
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3000000000000030,
      "definition": {
        "title": "Lane Pool Health",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 3000000000000031,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "**Backend lane pool.** Each (shard, interlay) holds N backend Redis connections. Saturation shows up as rising `acquire_wait` and growing `waiters`. Init failures point at backend reachability.",
              "background_color": "gray",
              "font_size": "12",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 3,
              "height": 7
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3000000000000032,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Lanes open by shard",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "max",
                "value"
              ],
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "alias": "Lanes open",
                      "formula": "lanes"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "lanes",
                      "query": "sum:eden.proxy.lane_pool_lanes_open{$interlay_uuid,$eden_node_uuid} by {shard_id}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "warm",
